{"tid":1176240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商界想加入反送中　社運友唔通想佢地黎遊行？　用咩方式反先得架","createTime":"2019-05-29T05:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:53:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f49ff35c9dfd81c15ef20a20672a430c7315864","tid":1176240,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157146608962357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157146608962357&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=4b537e1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157146608962357</a><br />\n<br />\n商界：「好，我想加入反送中。」<br />\n社運友：「好！咁你黎遊行啦！」<br />\n<br />\n其實你想佢地用咩方式反先得架...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgYos6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgYos6E.png&h=92578b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157095942662357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157095942662357&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=cb2edd4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157095942662357</a><br />\n<br />\n商界不是不想反對逃犯條例，可是他們一早無席，你要玩議會抗爭他們沒角色，玩議會外啦啦隊「為議員打氣」念力社運他們會覺得無聊，而且商界從來都不是湊人數燒時間的。所以根本沒介入空間。<br />\n<br />\n出錢買念力，或者幫議員助理出糧，或者買義工搞地區工作，商界根本不需要這種事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGraham Tse: 商界一向要免費午餐. <img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t52/1/16/1f923.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft52%2F1%2F16%2F1f923.png&h=8846d5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t52/1/16/1f923.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft52%2F1%2F16%2F1f923.png&h=8846d5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap: 去不到免費午餐，但至少有投資回報"},{"pid":"ee6d31412a6fb89e305f037560634b75e0d0d689","tid":1176240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7c9f616f6ca28efda33d2485fff59af09a5fe1","tid":1176240,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"好似王維基咁唔得咩？"}]}